[SPEAKER_02] Misliš moraš me staviti, ne moraš me, već da me nisi stavio.

95
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:42,240
[SPEAKER_02] A trener odlučuje.

96
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:42,799
[SPEAKER_02] Tako je.

97
00:20:42,960 --> 00:20:43,920
